Deployment1:
-----------
https://github.com/giantswarm/kubernetes-prometheus
Prometheus: kubectl get pods -n monitoring (http://127.0.0.1:9090/targets prometheus)
Alert-manager: kubectl port-forward -n monitoring <node-name> 9093.  (http://127.0.0.1:9093/#/alerts -- alert-manager)
Graphana: kubectl port-forward -n monitoring grafana-core-f796895df-4rt8m 3000


